- `incremental_rank` and `batch_rank` are calculated based on the durations of incremental and batch processing, respectively, for each data source;
- The query focuses on the top 3 iterations for each data source in terms of processing time;
- `access_count` represents the number of times users accessed the system during these iterations;
- The query ensures that only iterations with more than one user access event are considered.
